  <!-- Game Rules -->
  <section class="content-section bg-primary text-white text-center" id="game-rules">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-section-heading">
        <h2 class="text-secondary mb-0">Game Rules</h2>
        <h3 class="mb-5">Food Fight takes place over the course of five rounds, with each round being divided into two
          phases.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
          <span class="service-icon rounded-circle mx-auto mb-3">
            <i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i>
          </span>
          <h4>
            <strong>Start Of Game</strong>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-faded mb-0">Player order will be randomly determined and players will be presented with a
            character select screen. Players will sequentially select a character.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
          <span class="service-icon rounded-circle mx-auto mb-3">
            <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
          </span>
          <h4>
            <strong>The Shopping Phase</strong>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-faded mb-0">Random items will be generated across the map page.Items give players an increase
            to their attack value for the following battle phase. Each player will roll dice at the start of their turn
            to determine how many
            spaces they are allowed to move. Characters cannot pass through each other, so after a player has picked up
            an item, they can try and block another player from picking up an item.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-5 mb-md-0">
          <span class="service-icon rounded-circle mx-auto mb-3">
            <i class="fas fa-fist-raised"></i>
          </span>
          <h4>
            <strong>The Battle Phase</strong>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-faded mb-0">This phase of the round is a four way free-for-all turned based battle. The player
            will have the option to attack any of the other three players. Players will gain points based off what place
            they come in during the battle phase.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
          <span class="service-icon rounded-circle mx-auto mb-3">
            <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
          </span>
          <h4>
            <strong>Champion Of The Grocery Store</strong>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-faded mb-0">After five rounds have been completed the user with the most points will be
            delcared "Champion of the Grocery Store"</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

